Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------SUB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缘你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命是与红世之徒战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界真正的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要修复这城市的歪曲看来需要你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛裘莉小姐所说的密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼词朗诵者的助手是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  田中也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是我说的话才对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然是密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的坂井悠二呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井悠二…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…意外的很坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般不会用这种口气说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是担心被大家知道了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算刚才也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  必须去找吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事被她知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后受了很大的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得赶快解释
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算解释也没什么意义了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实终归是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌的圣庙差不多到了完成阶段了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  教授
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像火雾战士们完全不明白那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…看来那个的目的并不是扩大歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会出现歪曲也许是其他计划的副作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…因为「探耽求究」是个喜欢做无用功的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微去看下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  到底想让我做这种无聊的事到何时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启作和荣太还没到玻璃坛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍旧没有那痴呆教授的气息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明派出那么多磷子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来还有另一个火雾战士在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道和探耽求究有没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接去问不是更快些么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去问问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这些磷子的力量不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛裘莉说过又进来了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个…是这个的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个让吉田同学看到了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了…我也必须快点去玻璃坛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是…火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缘是火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…在这城市所发生的事情和坂井同学的事全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都知道了却还…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却还喜欢坂井同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经能一个人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…原来是悼词朗诵者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才在战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得感到一股子粗暴的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊…这不是老爷子们嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能松口气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎和神经病教授没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们也对感觉不到探耽求究的气息抱有疑问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底设置了什么机关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也想知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不是  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来怎么一副死样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这么说来你就是坂井悠二吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…没想到居然是密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了对不起那小姑娘的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么把她卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很适合作我们的协助者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适合？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这种随便的理由就把这个给她了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道突然看到了那些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会受到多么大的打击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学明明什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一定要拖她来我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎对你来说是相当重要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学是个温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个不可以来我们世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该一直待在原来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经身处无法回来的地方了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…把你卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然画面不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但首先得看清现实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…对对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那个自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对它的实体稍微有些眉目了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和吉田一美那种人没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不像夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会说那种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个自在式的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是利用城市的歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在空间里挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空间里挖洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬把拼板的其中一块拆下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说的话就容易理解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既明白又不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做这种事到底有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…探耽求究从很早以前就经常做莫名其妙的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  确实对城市有着影响
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以马上开始调律才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像昨天和你说明的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能协助我们进行调律吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说协助？继续将吉田同学卷进来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放着不管的话  城市会变得更加乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和卡姆辛先生约定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很对不起刚才逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「卡迪修的心室」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  什么也没发生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好像稍微有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…因为那个自在式的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城市里标下的印记不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说不能进行调律了的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  因为发生了很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦  玻璃坛启动了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城市上空的自在式某处有个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市中到处弥漫了的自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中到了一处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概在祭典主会场附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说自在式的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在祭典主会场的河边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是塔台那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来探耽求究把大部分是机器做成的磷子当作助手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「助人为乐」多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…本该想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那东西的话感觉不到气息也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒那个磷子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自在式也能破解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着这个  联络用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  马尔克希亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会说  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌的圣庙前言的数字控制在预计范围之内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来所接受委托的实验就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来就准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我所带来样品自在式进行预备实验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…火雾战士接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那里就自己想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先前往集中点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  别突然动手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布有歪曲存在之力的防御自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼呼呼…你们的攻击是无效的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始变形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…有什么意义么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天晓得…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  刚才的机关确实挺麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太危险了无法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神经病教授
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城市外面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…看来没打算躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得感觉不到气息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…但准备从哪里进来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很明显地在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  要上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探耽求究做事总是毫无意义的夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这个作战本身毫无意义也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特意从空中来是有意义的也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才说过那里的空间有一块拼板被拆掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那飞艇也许是最后的拼板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小男孩的说法也有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那机器人  去扰乱那空间不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正飞艇也有同样的机关啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算攻击也没效的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  万一真是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制造出那空间的自在法也会受到影响的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要接近那空间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要解开自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…还有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么意外的话我会一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话真想拒绝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不到悠二的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二…好远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  变形完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  火雾战士们放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是高潮和华丽的最后一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自在法解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往Van  Berry的街角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘着马儿去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管到哪都有伴奏  嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火雾战士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子在发神经呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你再随心所欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨碍我探究神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这帮思考停滞的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米诺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让他们瞧瞧珍藏已久的必杀技
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变得奇怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对只是想这么做而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直可以称为「双保险」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请避开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽快击落它的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？要动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷子要发飙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不战斗就大胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合不合体根本没什么意义嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有意义是由我来决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是来干啥的…那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学…是这么温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经治不好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…真正的我已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类？我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为身体和心都是这么的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢这样的坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…发动「卡迪修的心室」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  请想象你城市的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据这个来纠正歪曲  进行调律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从出生以来一直居住的这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个温暖的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二他不会和我一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔艾米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说有些做得过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探耽求究
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的工作可是事先准备而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验本身已经成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可没资格发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实  一定会顺利进行的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与怀念的威尔艾米娜重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.44,0:24:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她却敏感地察觉到了夏娜的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.66,0:24:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后她逼着夏娜做出了一个决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  无情的威尔艾米娜
